# MCP server credentials.
#
# context7 — works without a key for basic usage; sign up at https://context7.com
#            for higher rate limits + researchMode.
# magic-mcp — get a free key at https://21st.dev/magic — set in shell env or here.
# playwright — no key needed.
#
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and `source .env` before launching Claude Code,
# OR export in your shell profile.

# CONTEXT7_API_KEY=ctx7sk-...
# MAGIC_MCP_API_KEY=...
